msgstr "根据 Google Search Console 的点击次数返回效果最好的关键字，以及所选日期范围内的展示次数、点击率和平均排名。"

#: includes/abilities/analytics/class-get-top-keywords.php:90
msgid "Date range for which to fetch keyword data."
msgstr "获取关键字数据的日期范围。"

#: includes/abilities/analytics/class-get-top-keywords.php:97
msgid "Maximum number of keywords to return."
msgstr "要返回的关键字的最大数量。"

#: includes/abilities/analytics/class-get-top-keywords.php:171
