msgstr "搜索查询关键字。"

#: includes/abilities/analytics/class-get-top-keywords.php:175
msgid "Total clicks from Google Search Console."
msgstr "总点击次数来自 Google Search Console。"

#: includes/abilities/analytics/class-get-top-keywords.php:179
