#: includes/abilities/analytics/class-get-top-keywords.php:192
msgid "Position trend vs. the previous period. Provided by Rank Math PRO for tracked keywords."
msgstr "与上一时期相比的排名趋势。由 Rank Math PRO 为跟踪的关键字提供。"

#: includes/abilities/analytics/class-get-top-keywords.php:196
msgid "Whether this keyword is tracked in Rank Math PRO Rank Tracker."
msgstr "此关键字是否在 Rank Math PRO 排名跟踪器中跟踪。"

#: includes/abilities/analytics/class-get-top-keywords.php:200
msgid "Pages on your site that rank for this keyword. Provided by Rank Math PRO."
msgstr "您网站上为此关键字排名的页面。由 Rank Math PRO 提供。"

