msgstr "帖子标题。"

#: includes/abilities/analytics/class-get-top-keywords.php:214
msgid "Relative URL path of the page."
msgstr "页面的相对 URL 路径。"

#: includes/abilities/analytics/class-get-top-keywords.php:228
