#: includes/abilities/content-analysis/class-analyze-post-content.php:71
msgid "Analyze post content"
msgstr "分析帖子内容"

#: includes/abilities/content-analysis/class-analyze-post-content.php:72
msgid "Gathers the raw content, metadata, and list of on-page SEO tests for a saved post so an AI agent can run Rank Math's full on-page analysis itself, since the scoring engine only runs client-side. Use tests_to_run and content together with kb_link (the scoring rubric for all 24 tests) to evaluate each test and produce a per-test score, status, and fix message."
msgstr "收集原始内容、元数据和页面 SEO 列表测试已保存的帖子，以便 AI 代理可以自行运行 Rank Math 的完整页面分析，因为评分引擎仅运行客户端。将tests_to_run和内容与kb_link（所有24个测试的评分标准）一起使用来评估每个测试并生成每个测试的分数、状态和修复消息。"

#: includes/abilities/content-analysis/class-analyze-post-content.php:82
msgid "ID of the post to analyze."
msgstr "要分析的帖子的ID。"

#: includes/abilities/content-analysis/class-analyze-post-content.php:86
msgid "Optional focus keyword to analyze against, overriding the post's saved focus keyword."
msgstr "要分析的可选焦点关键字，覆盖帖子已保存的焦点关键字。"

#: includes/abilities/content-analysis/class-analyze-post-content.php:131
msgid "No post found with the given ID, or the post status is not supported."
msgstr "没有找到具有给定ID的帖子，或者帖子状态不受支持。"

#: includes/abilities/content-analysis/class-analyze-post-content.php:145
msgid "Evaluate each test ID in tests_to_run against the fields in content, using kb_link as the scoring rubric for how each test is scored. Return a per-test breakdown with score, max_score, status (pass/fail), and a message with a specific fix. For the contentHasTOC test, when suggesting a fix or drafting content, tell the user to insert the Rank Math Table of Contents block (block name rank-math/toc-block, available in the block inserter as \"Table of Contents\") right after the intro, instead of a manual list of links — it auto-generates from the post headings."
msgstr "评估每个测试ID test_to_run 针对内容中的字段，使用 kb_link 作为每个测试如何评分的评分标准。返回每个测试的详细信息，包括分数、最大分数、状态（通过/失败）以及包含特定修复的消息。对于 contentHasTOC 测试，当建议修复或起草内容时，告诉用户在介绍之后插入 Rank Math 目录块（块名称 rank-math/toc-block，在块插入器中可用作“目录”），而不是手动链接列表 - 它会从帖子标题自动生成。"

#: includes/abilities/content-analysis/class-get-seo-scores.php:67
msgid "Get SEO scores"
msgstr "获取 SEO 分数"

#: includes/abilities/content-analysis/class-get-seo-scores.php:68
msgid "Returns SEO scores and grades for posts. Before running, ask the user which posts they want to review: posts needing improvement (bad score), posts with no focus keyword, unscored posts, or simply the most recently modified posts. Use this to surface which posts need SEO attention without needing to know post IDs in advance."
msgstr "返回帖子的 SEO 分数和等级。在运行之前，询问用户他们想要查看哪些帖子：需要改进的帖子（分数不好）、没有焦点关键字的帖子、未评分的帖子或只是最近修改的帖子。使用此功能可以显示哪些帖子需要 SEO 关注，而无需提前知道帖子 ID。"

#: includes/abilities/content-analysis/class-get-seo-scores.php:78
msgid "Number of recently modified posts to retrieve. Defaults to 10, maximum 100."
msgstr "要检索的最近修改的帖子数量。默认为 10，最大为 100。"

#: includes/abilities/content-analysis/class-get-seo-scores.php:85
msgid "Post type to filter by (e.g. \"post\", \"page\"). Defaults to all public post types."
msgstr "要过滤的帖子类型（例如“帖子”、“页面”）。默认为所有公共帖子类型。"

#: includes/abilities/content-analysis/class-get-seo-scores.php:89
msgid "Ask the user which posts they want to review before running this ability. Available options: \"bad\" (score ≤ 50, needs improvement), \"good\" (score 51–80, ok), \"great\" (score > 80), \"empty-fk\" (no focus keyword set), \"unscored\" (never analyzed). If the user does not specify, omit this parameter to return the most recently modified posts."
msgstr "在运行此功能之前询问用户他们想要查看哪些帖子。可用选项：“差”（分数 ≤ 50，需要改进）、“好”（分数 51-80，还可以）、“很棒”（分数 > 80）、“empty-fk”（未设置焦点关键字）、“unscored”（从未分析过）。如果用户未指定，则省略此参数以返回最近修改的帖子。"

#: includes/abilities/content-analysis/class-get-seo-scores.php:308
#: includes/abilities/content-analysis/class-get-seo-scores.php:341
#: assets/admin/js/classic.js:1
